# DeckVault — TCG Collection Manager

Supported games: Yu-Gi-Oh, Pokemon, Digimon.

Goals: track collection, import/export (including file backup), multi-collection, anime side collection, proxy print, optional cloud sync + live collaboration.

## Product scope (current)

**In scope:** Auth (optional cloud), Collection views, Search/Quick Add, Import CSV/decklist, Export, Collection manager, Anime collection (local), Proxy print, Settings + **JSON backup/restore**, Share collection + Live presence (Supabase).

**Out of scope (removed):** Deck builder product, Wishlist product, in-collection Folders, Tags product, Price history / portfolio graphs, Trading, Notifications feed, community Phase 4 (friends, comments, etc.).

## Roadmap (slim)

**Now:** Harden Live collab, keep backup-by-file, polish collection UX, API safety.

**Later (optional):** Stats summaries, bulk edit beyond delete, performance (binder virtualization).
